Submit a potential project on TrendX

To discover and bring online more quality projects and take advantage of DAO. Any user can submit a project that they think has potential, and have everyone vote to determine whether the project is good or bad. The scout who submits a project and passes the review has the right and obligation to maintain and edit the project. If the project is later on IDO or INO on TrendX platform, the scout who found the project will get the fundraising share.

What are the benefits to stake Token?

Staking Income

Users with pledged Token will gain benefits. The longer they hold Token, the more the benefits

Governance Income

Users with pledged Token will have the right to vote, thus gaining governance benefits through voting

Referral Income

2% of the raised funds will be distributed to the users with pledged Token
